      <title>印度议会通过有争议的穆斯林财产法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/india-parliament-passes-controversial-muslim-property-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度议会通过了一项有争议的数十年的法律，该法律涉及了一项有争议的数十年法律，该法律是为了宗教和慈善目的而捐赠的穆斯林拥有的财产，这两家房屋都在漫长的辩论之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/india-parliament-passes-controversial-muslim-property-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:22:26 GMT</pubDate>
