      <title>曼谷清除了倒塌的塔的碎片，数十个仍缺失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bangkok-clears-debris-of-collapsed-tower-as-dozens-still-missing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼谷市政府开始清理上周地震坠毁的塔楼的碎屑，因为在数十名工人中发现幸存者的希望仍然被困在几乎已经结束了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bangkok-clears-debris-of-collapsed-tower-as-dozens-still-missing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
