      <title>布加勒斯特市市长出价，担任Tiktok领导的竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bucharest-mayor-bids-for-presidency-with-tiktok-led-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布加勒斯特市市长尼古斯·丹（Nicusor Dan）注意到观众中的每个人都停止听他的声音，因此获得了公民奖。他们都是疯狂地在手机上滚动的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bucharest-mayor-bids-for-presidency-with-tiktok-led-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
